Introduction

Choi Byung-chan is a South Korean singer and actor under New Way Company.

Byunchan debuted as a member of VICTON on November 9, 2016, with the mini album 'Voice To New World.'

In May 2019, he, alongside fellow member Han Seung Woo, became a contestant on the survival show Produce X 101. However, on July 11, it was announced he would be leaving the show due to health issues.
